Class Wave

  • java.lang.Object
    • estuary.model.Entity
      • estuary.model.MovingEntity
        • estuary.model.Wave
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Movable, java.io.Serializable

    public class Wave
extends MovingEntity
    A wave is generated by a shore threat. When a wave collides with anything, it is removed. When a wave collides with a shore or seawall, is damages that entity.
